HEADWORD: Lordlike
<hw>Lord"like`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[2d <ets>lord</ets> +
<ets>like</ets>. Cf. <er>Lordly</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Befitting or like a lord; lordly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Haughty; proud; insolent; arrogant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lordliness</ent>⟦br⟧
